title: Saagar
subTitle: Raja secretly loves Mona, but she is in love with Ravi. However, Ravi's grandmother disapproves of their relationship and asks Mona to forget him and marry someone else.

title: Rakta Bandhan
subTitle: Chandan is found dead by his twin brother Trishul, who is a dacoit. In a bid to turn a new leaf and leave the criminal life behind, Trishul assumes his brother's identity.

title: Baat Ban Jaye
subTitle: Nisha, a wealthy woman in charge of her family business, does not want to marry a rich man. She falls in love with Suraj Singh, a wedding singer and dancer, without realising that he has other plans.

title: Mome Ki Gudiya
subTitle: Ravi falls in love with Sheel but is shocked to learn that her marriage is fixed with his father. Even after his father steps back and Ravi gets married to Sheel, dark secrets loom over the newlyweds.

title: Shiv Sati Vivah
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Sheshnaag
subTitle: Pritam and Banu, two shape-shifting snakes in human form, seek protection from a young man when an evil priest tries to hunt them down and use them in a ritual for wealth and immortality.

title: Tum Haseen Main Jawaan
subTitle: Sunil, a navy officer, falls for Anuradha. However, things get complicated when Ranjeet, Anuradha's admirer, claims that she is a single mother.

title: Amrit
subTitle: A widowed man and woman face abuse from their respective children and seek comfort from each other instead.

title: Kohram
subTitle: When a teacher is killed by two village tyrants, Thakur and Kalia, his brother Arjun swears to avenge him. Years later, Arjun kills Thakur and then joins forces with his brother's sons to face Kalia.

title: Izzat
subTitle: Constable Ram Chandra teaches his son Siddharth to be a diligent policeman and lead his life with honesty and dignity. Siddharth follows his advice until circumstances force him to leave his ideals.

title: Chitchor
subTitle: When Geeta's sister arranges her wedding with a young engineer, their father mistakenly brings the wrong man home. However, as love blossoms between the two, the arrival of a letter startles everyone.

title: Chitchor
subTitle: When Geeta's sister arranges her wedding with a young engineer, their father mistakenly brings the wrong man home. However, as love blossoms between the two, the arrival of a letter startles everyone.

title: Videsh
subTitle: A drug lord escapes from India to Britain, assuming the identity of Swami Prem Babu to continue his illegal activities. When he learns that CBI Inspector Prasad Sinha is investigating him, he kidnaps Sinha's daughter.

title: Nazrana
subTitle: Rajat, a music director, and Mukta, a dancer, get married against the wishes of Mukta's father. Things take a turn when Mukta suspects her husband of having an affair with Sheetal, an upcoming model.

title: Taraana
subTitle: The budding love between Shyam, who belongs to a rich family, and Radha, a poor woman, meets with the disapproval of their guardians.

title: Ankhiyon Ke Jharokhon Se
subTitle: College competitors Lily and Arun gradually fall in love and soon, both their parents approve of their relationship. However, their lives turn upside down when she is diagnosed with leukaemia.

title: Bhagwaan Dada
subTitle: Bhagwaan, a reformed criminal, rescues Swaroop, a naive villager. Swaroop rescues Bijli, a young woman targeted by Shambu. The situation regresses when Shambu decides to exact revenge.

title: Ek Hi Bhool
subTitle: Ram's affair with Sadhana's close friend leads to their painful separation and a shattered marriage. Years later, their son Raju attempts to reunite them.

title: Mehbooba
subTitle: Suraj, a singer, takes refuge from a storm in a rest house. During his stay, he has a strange feeling that he has been there before and recalls memories of being with a woman called Ratna.

title: Saudagar
subTitle: Moti betrays his loyal wife and business partner, Majubee, to marry his true love, Phoolbanu. However, his selfish act unleashes unforeseen consequences that upend his life.

title: Dadagiri
subTitle: Barkha, a young heiress, is abused by her uncle and his family for her inheritance. Later, she runs away but is captured and taken back to her abusive relatives by her mother's ex-lover, Dharma.

title: Dadagiri
subTitle: Barkha, a young heiress, is abused by her uncle and his family for her inheritance. Later, she runs away but is captured and taken back to her abusive relatives by her mother's ex-lover, Dharma.

title: Deewaangee
subTitle: Shekhar's pursuit of easy wealth puts his family in peril when they're taken hostage as a fallout from his ill-fated choices.

title: Hum Paanch
subTitle: Thakur Vir Pratap Singh, a landlord, rules over a town with an iron fist and crushes anybody who opposes him. However, unable to put up with his atrocities, five men join hands to destroy him.

title: Khel Mohabbat Ka
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Agent Vinod
subTitle: Vinod, a flamboyant secret agent, is assigned to investigate the kidnapping of an eminent scientist. Enlisting the help of the scientist's daughter, Anju, he confronts the abductors.

title: Bramachari
subTitle: Brahmachari, who was abandoned as a child, lives in a mortgaged house with 12 young orphans. Things take a turn when he saves a young woman from dying.

title: Khoon Bhari Maang
subTitle: Widowed Aarti falls prey to Sanjay's vicious plan of getting married to him. Later, with the help of her best friend Nandini, he drowns Aarti and seizes her wealth but she survives and seeks revenge.

title: Meri Aawaz Suno
subTitle: Sushil Kumar, a police officer, is charged with the task of apprehending a gang of kidnappers, who only target women. However, doing so not only threatens his identity and life but also his family's.

title: Mera Gaon Mera Desh
subTitle: When Ajit, a former prisoner, learns of Jabbar who is terrorising the people of his village, he decides to stand up against him. However, things take a turn when Jabbar abducts Ajit's lover.

title: Kundan
subTitle: Thakur Shamsher Singh, a wealthy criminal, tries to befriend a newly-appointed police officer in order to gain his favour, only to find out that the policeman is immune to his tactics.
